ll wise vis a vis the product you make (I.e. you'll be able to have a better chance of making nicer stuff at the same skill level), but it would behoove you to get thru banded as quickly as possible on cheap combines in anticipation of needing more money (overall) to get to a high level in smithing. <br>
<br>
