<br>
For smithing skill ups depend on the highest one of  either STR/WIS/INT.   And do not forget your CHA gear!!  Lower your prices to purchase, and increase your sell back price.<br>
<br>
With 110 cha, and an INT in the 120 - 150 range, I capped banded relatively cheaply on my enchantress, about 400pp from 20 to 175 skill.  I did it the hard way with the pally.<br>
<br>
And *get a Gearlock Hammer*!!!!  The % skill increase dramatically increases your success rate, more items made == more PP on sell back.<br>
<br>
All in all, I cannot wait until the next patch.  I will be able to make my cultural armor, and prance about in seasick green armor, with nice AC and Stats.<br>
